column2: awake in the middle of the night
I forgot to take Zoloft for like 2 days and now I'm getting brain zaps
I've been feeling better every day
makes me question my whole life
making myself get out of bed
Not sure Im going to be willing to go for a week feeling like this
the only reason I haven't downed all these antidepressants is because sertraline overdose rarely results in death
feel like complete and utter crap
I'm determined to not become a ravenous asshole
